pages.pageText: In the absence of Commander Jared Kurth, I have assumed command of Fort Tethana. Your terms may sound generous, but the rumors surrounding Commander Kurth's disappearance are very ominous portents for those who join the Viamontian forces. I do not consider your current proposal sufficient to take such a risk with the men under my command. This is not to say that there is no possibility for a future alliance, but you will need to substantially improve your proposal for it to outweigh the possible negatives of an alliance with Sanamar.
